articles.title: Elena Rybakina confirms rise by beating Aryna Sabalenka to win Indian Wells - The Guardian
articles.description: An epic tiebreak put the Wimbledon champion Elena Rybakina on her way to beating Aryna Sabalenka 7-6 (11), 6-4 in Indian Wells
